            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chopped pepper</strong>, <strong>ground smoked paprika</strong>,<strong> ground coriander</strong>, <strong>dried oregano</strong>,<strong> chilli flakes </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!)<strong> </strong>and your<strong> white long grain rice </strong>to the dish</p><p>Add 225ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[300ml] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[450ml]</span> <strong>boiled water </strong>with the<strong> chicken stock mix </strong>and a pinch of<strong> salt </strong>and<strong> pepper</strong></p><p>Cover with a lid and put the dish in the oven for 25-30 min or until the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!)</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1722521969139-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1722521969139-x400.jpg",
