          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1722521969139-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>drained sweetcorn </strong>to a serving bowl with <strong>half </strong>the <strong>chopped coriander </strong>(you'll use the rest later!), the juice of <strong>half</strong> your <strong>lime[s] </strong>and a drizzle of<strong> olive oil </strong>then crumble over your <strong>feta</strong></p><p>Add a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>esquites</strong></p><p>Cut the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>lime</strong> into 1 wedge per person</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1722521972681-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1722521972681-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1722521972681-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1722521972681-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1722521972681-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once everything's cooked through, remove the dish from the oven</p><p>Shred the <strong>cooked chicken</strong> apart using two forks and fluff the rice<strong> </strong>– this is your <strong>smoky coriander chicken & rice</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1722521976226-x200.jpg",
