          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1722521976226-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>To serve, garnish the <strong>smoky coriander chicken & rice </strong>with the <strong>remaining chopped coriander </strong>and a<strong> lime wedge</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>esquites </strong>to the side</p><p>Dig in!</p>",
      "order": 8,
